Title: 087: Business Intelligence – The Role of Data Visualization
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Tableau and Qlik Intrapreneur, Deepak Prasad. You will hear about Business Intelligence, particularly in business decision-making through data insights, learn about dashboard design best practices, and answering questions through interactive dashboards.
